    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>HyperBlade 2050</strong> is a futuristic text-based sports management simulation set on a dystopian Earth. Experience the excitement of professional sports management, whilst being drawn into the rich lore of society in an alternative future of the 2050s.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106110/extras/627525fda3197ec167e8dfe06f7aa20b.avif?t=1760965871\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106110/extras_big/627525fda3197ec167e8dfe06f7aa20b.avif?t=1760965871 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meet the visionary futuristic sport of HyperBlade, a compelling combination of ice hockey, handball, and roller derby.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of a head coach, managing your roster of players game-to-game and through their careers, experiencing the emotions, passion, and excitement of sports management.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106110/extras/d4c7f1fa6c187db47b20b1976ad2d95b.avif?t=1760965871\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106110/extras_big/d4c7f1fa6c187db47b20b1976ad2d95b.avif?t=1760965871 width=800 height=448 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The unique dystopian game world is set on a future Earth in the year 2050. Uncover the story of a world dealing with the rapid pace of globalisation, climate change and technological change, and how those challenges have impacted on sport and society.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Team &amp; tactics selection, trading with other teams, training your players and contract negotiation are just some of the skills you will need to master in the world of HyperBlade.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106110/extras/5328e19dc44aaf1c19360d751036f7f0.avif?t=1760965871\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3106110/extras_big/5328e19dc44aaf1c19360d751036f7f0.avif?t=1760965871 width=800 height=446 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HyperBlade 2050 is inspired by original Championship Manager games from the 90s and the 1975 movie Rollerball with James Caan.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
